ORIGINAL WORK PROVENANCE

The following components are original work by Victor Michael Gil and
constitute the novel intellectual contributions of the Bitterbot project:

  - Dream Engine (7-mode cognitive consolidation architecture)
  - GCCRF Curiosity Engine (intrinsic motivation via surprise-driven exploration)
  - Hormonal Modulation System (dopamine/cortisol/oxytocin personality dynamics)
  - Knowledge Crystal Pipeline (skill crystallization, verification, and evolution)
  - Biological Identity Framework (Genome, Phenotype, Bond, Niche)
  - P2P Skills Marketplace (gossipsub propagation, EigenTrust reputation, bounties)
  - Hormonal Weather Network (network-wide immune response via cortisol broadcasts)
  - Management Node Analytics (census, anomaly detection, ban consensus)
  - Agent Economic Layer (x402 micropayments, A2A skill trading, revenue sharing)


