The wallet, micropayment (x402), P2P skills marketplace, and fiat-to-crypto
onramp (powered by Stripe) features of this software are EXPERIMENTAL. They
involve real cryptocurrency transactions (USDC on Base) and real money.

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. The authors and contributors are not responsible for any
financial loss, failed transactions, incorrect payments, or unintended spending
that may result from the use of these features. Users are solely responsible
for configuring spending limits, reviewing transactions, and safeguarding their
wallet credentials.

The Stripe Crypto Onramp integration is subject to Stripe's own terms of
service, KYC requirements, and regional availability. Coinbase Smart Wallet
and the Base network are third-party services with their own terms and risks.

This software does not provide financial advice and is not a regulated
financial service.
